e signed a two-year contract with the Cypriot club [[AEK Larnaca]]. However, in January 2008 moved to [[Nea Salamis Famagusta FC|Nea Salamina]].\n\n==External links==\n* {{NFT player|pid=7403}}\n\n{{Zimbabwe Squad 2006 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kaondera, Shingayi}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean footballers]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwe international footballers]]\n[[Category:2006 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:AEP Paphos FC players]]\n[[Category:Nea Salamis Famagusta FC players]]\n[[Category:AEK Larnaca FC players]]\n[[Category:Digenis Akritas Morphou FC players]]\n[[Category:Chalkanoras Idaliou players]]\n[[Category:AEK Kouklia F.C. players]]\n[[Category:G\u00f3rnik Zabrze players]]\n[[Category:Gaziantepspor footballers]]\n[[Category:Ekstraklasa players]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:Cypriot First Division players]]\n[[Category:Cypriot Second Division players]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Cyprus]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Poland]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate sportspeople in Poland]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n\n\n{{Zimbabwe-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Zimbabwean footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Zimbabwean footballer\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shingayi_Kaondera"}
{"title_page": "Bruce Kangwa", "text_new": "{{short description|Zimbabwean footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name           = Bruce Kangwa\n|image          = \n|image_size     = \n|caption        = \n|fullname       = \n|birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1988|2|24|df=y}}\n|birth_place    = \n|height         = {{height|m=1.65}}<ref name = \"NFT\"/>\n|position       = [[Defender (association football)|Left back]]\n|currentclub    = [[Azam F.C.|Azam]]\n|clubnumber     = \n|youthyears1    = \n|youthclubs1    = \n|years1         = 2009\u20132016\n|clubs1         = [[Highlanders F.C.|Highlanders]]\n|caps1          = \n|goals1         = \n|years2         = 2016\u2013\n|clubs2         = [[Azam F.C.|Azam]]\n|caps2          = \n|goals2         = \n|nationalyears1 = 2009\u2013\n|nationalteam1  = [[Zimbabwe national football team|Zimbabwe]]\n|nationalcaps1  = 11\n|nationalgoals1 = 0\n|club-update    = 13:08, 21 January 2017 (UTC)\n|ntupdate       = 13:08, 21 January 2017 (UTC)\n}}\n\n'''Bruce Kangwa''' (born 24 February 1988) is a Zimbabwean international [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Azam F.C.|Azam]] as a [[Defender (association football)|left back]].\n\n==Career==\nKangwa has played for [[Highlanders F.C.|Highlanders]] and [[Azam F.C.|Azam]].<ref name = \"NFT\">{{cite web |url=http://www.national-football-teams.com/player/33649.html |title=Player profile |website=National-Football-Teams.com |accessdate=21 January 2017}}</ref>\n\nHe made his international debut in 2009,<ref name = \"NFT\"/> and was named in the squad for the [[2017 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zimnews.net/who-is-in-zim-line-up-squad-for-afcon-2017/|title=Zimbabwe Africa Cup of Nations, Afcon 2017 squad, List of 23 final names for Gabon soccer tournament|accessdate=21 January 2017|publisher=Zim News}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Zimbabwe squad 2017 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kangwa, Bruce}}\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean footballers]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwe international footballers]]\n[[Category:Highlanders F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Azam F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Association football fullbacks]]\n[[Category:2017 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate sportspeople in Tanzania]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Tanzania]]\n\n\n{{Zimbabwe-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name           = Bruce Kangwa\n|image          = \n|image_size     = \n|caption        = \n|fullname       = \n|birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1988|2|24|df=y}}\n|birth_place    = \n|height         = {{height|m=1.65}}<ref name = \"NFT\"/>\n|position       = [[Defender (association football)|Left back]]\n|currentclub    = [[Azam F.C.|Azam]]\n|clubnumber     = \n|youthyears1    = \n|youthclubs1    = \n|years1         = 2009\u20132016\n|clubs1         = [[Highlanders F.C.|Highlanders]]\n|caps1          = \n|goals1         = \n|years2         = 2016\u2013\n|clubs2         = [[Azam F.C.|Azam]]\n|caps2          = \n|goals2         = \n|nationalyears1 = 2009\u2013\n|nationalteam1  = [[Zimbabwe national football team|Zimbabwe]]\n|nationalcaps1  = 11\n|nationalgoals1 = 0\n|club-update    = 13:08, 21 January 2017 (UTC)\n|ntupdate       = 13:08, 21 January 2017 (UTC)\n}}\n\n'''Bruce Kangwa''' (born 24 February 1988) is a Zimbabwean international [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Azam F.C.|Azam]] as a [[Defender (association football)|left back]].\n\n==Career==\nKangwa has played for [[Highlanders F.C.|Highlanders]] and [[Azam F.C.|Azam]].<ref name = \"NFT\">{{cite web |url=http://www.national-football-teams.com/player/33649.html |title=Player profile |website=National-Football-Teams.com |accessdate=21 January 2017}}</ref>\n\nHe made his international debut in 2009,<ref name = \"NFT\"/> and was named in the squad for the [[2017 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zimnews.net/who-is-in-zim-line-up-squad-for-afcon-2017/|title=Zimbabwe Africa Cup of Nations, Afcon 2017 squad, List of 23 final names for Gabon soccer tournament|accessdate=21 January 2017|publisher=Zim News}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Zimbabwe squad 2017 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kangwa, Bruce}}\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean footballers]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwe international footballers]]\n[[Category:Highlanders F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Azam F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Association football fullbacks]]\n[[Category:2017 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriate sportspeople in Tanzania]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Tanzania]]\n\n\n{{Zimbabwe-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Zimbabwean footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"association football player\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruce_Kangwa"}
